{"tid":2386261,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"探子: 港人大流散 由BNO開始","createTime":"2021-01-29T12:59:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T15:00:11.000Z","uid":251732,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"70ee8f94a48878da9d770a1842f18ef792b71edc","tid":2386261,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:59:51.000Z","msg":"🛂英聯邦國家快啲撤僑<br />\n雙重國籍問題郁到好多香港有錢佬<br />\n大走資預備正式爆發<br />\n不嬲雙重國籍都係違反中共憲法<br />\n只不過係大陸隻眼開隻眼閉<br />\n中共憲法同基本法其實唔可以共存<br />\n成班讀法律嘅都唔知讀咗咩出嚟😂<br />\n#探子 @infoshk"},{"pid":"92621ebb374e24ba7259ffc57afc9020ec8fa1b9","tid":2386261,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:42:25.000Z","msg":"push 1"},{"pid":"6a32106423718d0669ca94f3272fb4c1df6358e1","tid":2386261,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:43:07.000Z","msg":"🛂探子提出反制措施<br />\n出境香港嘅時候使用身分證<br />\n或回鄉證等其他有效的旅遊證件<br />\n入境其他國家包括英聯邦國家<br />\n即可使用BNO作為有效證件<br />\nBNO作為英聯邦承認之旅遊證件<br />\n任何英聯邦國家亦會提供外交協助<br />\n尋找任何英聯邦國家的領事館或領事<br />\n亦可獲得協助<br />\n在英國尚未脫歐之前<br />\n歐盟亦會協助BNO之人士<br />\n#探子 @infoshk"},{"pid":"2ffa06686479414eb49c68a25cd5794c0f00b537","tid":2386261,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:43:19.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"19e3dcd686c2bcf8cf7eb73ba31d80fff34c61ab","tid":2386261,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:44:37.000Z","msg":"push 2"},{"pid":"aa3dffaa1d529068fd8ee7eed55debe4e8179598","tid":2386261,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:45:55.000Z","msg":"push 3"},{"pid":"049adcf95a7755385866b5ff425ea68699ae7858","tid":2386261,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:46:56.000Z","msg":"push 4"},{"pid":"68ab9abc132f3b72f1131f277c77c5760f9c2d86","tid":2386261,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:47:15.000Z","msg":"push 5"},{"pid":"8fd5fc39